name: India in a nutshell
description: This picture was taken during a team photoshoot for Tezos India team featuring Bangalore palace and a Statue of Dr. Bhimrao Ambedkar (Chief architect of constitution of India) holding Constitution in his hand. If you look closely, you can also see Indian national symbol on the palace which says "Satyameva Jayate" meaning 'Truth Alone Triumphs'.
